This code works in python 3.6


sudo port install py36-tkinter sqlite3-tcl

Install pip:
curl https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py -o get-pip.py
sudo python3.6 get-pip.py --user
sudo python3.6 -m pip install --user numpy scipy matplotlib ipython jupyter pandas sympy nose

For the new python3.6 version you should also replace in energyCalibProgram.py the following names:
 - Replace NavToolbar2TkAgg with NavToolbar2Tk
 - Replace NavigationToolbar2TkAgg with NavigationToolbar2Tk

How to run it:
 python3.6 energyCalibProgram.py 


ToTest:

sudo port install py36-tkinter sqlite3-tcl py36-numpy py36-scipy py36-matplotlib py36-ipython py36-jupyter py36-pandas py36-sympy py36-nose



